 Fix: Add `role=\"table\"`, `role=\"row\"`, and `role=\"cell\"` to table structure\n\n3. **MINOR - Pagination missing total pages in text** (Content Author)\n   - Users need context about pagination scope\n   - Fix: Update page links to show \"Page X of Y\"\n\n4. **MINOR - Sort state indicators only visual** (Content Author)\n   - Screen readers miss sort state information\n   - Fix: Add text indicators for sort direction\n\n---\n\n## Recommended Fixes\n\n**For Front-End Dev:**\n1. Update sort header buttons with `aria-sort` attribute:\n```jsx\n<button \n  aria-sort={sortKey === col.key ? sortDir : 'none'}\n  // existing props...\n>\n```\n\n2. Add semantic roles to table structure:\n```jsx\n<div role=\"table\" aria-label=\"Employee directory\">\n  <div role=\"rowgroup\">\n    <div role=\"row\">\n      {COLUMNS.map(col => (\n        <div role=\"columnheader\" key={col.key} role=\"cell\">\n          {/* existing content */}\n        </div>\n      ))}\n    </div>\n    {/* data rows */}\n    {pageData.map(row => (\n      <div role=\"row\" key={row.id}>\n        {Object.values(row).map((value, idx) => (\n          <div role=\"cell\" key={idx}>{value}</div>\n        ))}\n      </div>\n    ))}\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n**For Content Author:**\n1. Update pagination to show total pages:\n```jsx\n<a {...props}>{i + 1} of {totalPages}</a>\n```\n\n2. Add text indicators to sort headers:\n```jsx\n{col.label}\n<span aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  {sortKey === col.key ? (sortDir === 'asc' ? ' \u25b2' : ' \u25bc') : ' \u21c5'}\n</span>\n<span className=\"sr-only\">\n  {sortKey === col.key ? \n    (sortDir === 'asc' ? 'Sorted ascending' : 'Sorted descending') : \n    'Not sorted'}\n</span>\n```",
